<C>__{sidney}
<D>__{i have no idea.}
<C>__{man}
<D>__{scary night, isn't it? with the murders and all, it's like right out of a horror movie or something.}
<C>__{sidney}
<D>__{aha, randy, you gave yourself away. are you calling from work? tatum's on her way over.}
