<D>__{don't start. you know i don't watch that shit.}
<C>__{man}
<D>__{and why is that?}
<C>__{sidney}
<P>__{(playing along)}
<D>__{because they're all the same. it's always some stupid killer stalking some big breasted girl who can't act who always runs up the stairs when she should be going out the front door. they're ridiculous.}
<A>__{a brief silence.}
